byline.contributor: Julie Hirschfeld Davis contributed reporting from Washington.

abstract: American analysts cannot predict how nuclear deal will impact Iranian politics.
lead_paragraph: While agreeing the talks are pivotal, American experts cannot predict the political impact of an accord on Tehran’s complex internal politics.

headline.main: After Nuclear Agreement, Analysts Weigh Deal’s Effects on Iranian Politics
